The '''[[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]] era''', sometimes referred to as the '''Classic era''', takes place between [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] (the [[Battle of Toprawa]]) and [[4 ABY/Legends|4 ABY]] (the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]]), and into events after the battle until [[5 ABY/Legends|5 ABY]].<ref>{{Blog|holocron|24|Star Wars Eras}}</ref>

The events of the [[original trilogy]] ([[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|Episode IV ''A New Hope'']], [[Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back|Episode V ''The Empire Strikes Back'']], and [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']]) take place during this era.

